title: Symbotic acquires autonomous forklift maker Fox Robotics
description:
Most of Fox Robotics' customers are not Symbotic customers, but it appears the two companies share one large customer.

The post Symbotic acquires autonomous forklift maker Fox Robotics appeared first on The Robot Report.
